question: Great lyric choice! Question of the day - where are you from and what languages do you speak? 💕
answer: Thanks 😊 I’m from Germany, my mom is German, but my dad is from Hungary and I used to spend all my holidays there. I can only speak a little bit of Hungarian though, it’s quite difficult to learn. Apart from that I speak German (duh), in school I studied English, Latin and French and in uni I took a few Spanish courses. What languages do you speak?
